{"tid":2221250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[當年今日] 消息指警方已出橡膠子彈，學聯呼籲各位參與佔領行動的市民全面撤離","createTime":"2020-09-28T08:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T09:26:44.000Z","uid":5843,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"88359c05064f4a395782fbbfc5b526b823eed468","tid":2221250,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:31:49.000Z","msg":"【學聯呼籲，市民全面撒離】22:10<br />\n<br />\n因有消息指警方已出橡膠子彈，學聯呼籲各位參與佔領行動的市民全面撤離。但我們強調學聯大台必運作至最後！我們要求警方必須讓示威者安全離開，不加阻撓。<br />\n面對政權刻意引發與市民之間的戰爭，我們必須保留實力。警方今日刻意濫用武力驅趕示威者，定必激發更多市民參與抗爭及不合作運動！<br />\n<br />\n希望在於人民，改變始於抗爭！保留力量，擇日再會！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkfs1958/photos/a.433111302871/10152468383712872/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkfs1958%2Fphotos%2Fa.433111302871%2F10152468383712872%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=7e2601e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkfs1958/photos/a.433111302871/10152468383712872/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n//歷史在不斷的重複⋯//"},{"pid":"bf8165910b98d433c5eac2666b5b36b247e31a51","tid":2221250,"uid":68689,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:38:21.000Z","msg":"14年出膠子彈就已經好大件事<br />\n估唔到19年半年內出哂膠子彈,tg,水炮車,真槍"},{"pid":"4f1984622901909d81d5f48cd81d9495a78e3398","tid":2221250,"uid":5843,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"bf8165910b98d433c5eac2666b5b36b247e31a51","tid":2221250,"uid":68689,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:38:21.000Z","msg":"14年出膠子彈就已經好大件事<br />\n估唔到19年半年內出哂膠子彈,tg,水炮車,真槍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"最癲係有一班勇士呢啲所有野都唔驚，繼續為香港奮戰"},{"pid":"b4274906d708a8cd3dfce3f508734548e5554ab3","tid":2221250,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4f1984622901909d81d5f48cd81d9495a78e3398","tid":2221250,"uid":5843,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"bf8165910b98d433c5eac2666b5b36b247e31a51","tid":2221250,"uid":68689,"like":10